    {
      "id": "optimistic_8_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_8",
      "description": "A solid, honest driver that offers a lot to enjoy for someone looking for a usable classic rather than a perfect show car. It\u2019s in fair condition, with noticeable cosmetic wear and signs of age, but it still presents decently and has the kind of character that makes it easy to appreciate. A great fit for someone who wants an affordable entry point into ownership and doesn\u2019t mind a car that shows it\u2019s been used.",
