      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "Priced at $33,900, this vehicle is in good overall condition and should make a solid, dependable driver for its next owner. It runs and drives as it should, with a clean appearance inside and out and the kind of normal wear you\u2019d expect from a well-kept used vehicle rather than anything excessive. Overall, it presents well, has been cared for, and should appeal to someone looking for a reliable, good-condition car without paying top-tier money for a mint example.",
      "price": 33900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_7_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_7",
      "description": "$47,500 - Beautiful mint-condition example that\u2019s been exceptionally well cared for and presents wonderfully throughout. This is the kind of car that immediately stands out for its cleanliness, overall finish, and how well it\u2019s been kept, while still being an honest, ready-to-enjoy driver rather than something overhyped. If you\u2019ve been looking for a truly top-tier car that you can be proud to own and enjoy right away, this one is absolutely worth a look.",
      "price": 47500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "Clean, honest good-condition example that presents well overall and should make a solid, enjoyable driver for the next owner. The exterior shows nicely with the kind of light cosmetic wear, minor blemishes, and age-related imperfections you\u2019d expect from a well-kept used vehicle, but nothing that takes away from its overall appeal. Inside, it appears tidy and well cared for, with normal signs of use consistent with age and mileage. This is not a mint showpiece, but it is a straightforward, good-quality car that offers attractive presentation and dependable everyday enjoyment.",
      "price": 34900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and ready for its next chapter, this vehicle is a practical choice for anyone seeking affordable transportation or a solid project opportunity. It shows clear signs of age and wear, but it offers straightforward value at an accessible price point. A sensible option for a handy owner, first-time buyer, or anyone needing inexpensive wheels without unnecessary extras.",
      "price": 4950.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Reliable, affordable, and ready for its next owner. This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a great option if you want budget-friendly transportation without a lot of fuss. It\u2019s been a dependable runaround and would suit a first-time buyer, commuter, or someone looking for a handy project. Priced fairly for what it is, and represented honestly by a seller who believes in straightforward deals.",
      "price": 6900.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid budget-friendly driver/project with a strong mechanical foundation and plenty of usable life left. The engine starts up, runs, and pulls well, the transmission goes through the gears, and the chassis feels like a great candidate for someone who wants affordable transportation or a hands-on weekend build. It shows wear consistent with age and use, but it remains a straightforward, honest car with good parts value and real potential. If you want an inexpensive entry point into ownership with room to improve over time, this one makes a compelling case.",
      "price": 6800.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    }
